            <title>[SOLR-12762] SolrCloudTestCase.clusterShape should check for active slices instead of all slices</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-12762</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;SolrCloudTestCase.clusterShare should assert against the active slices, based on the javadoc and usage but it instead checks for all slices.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
