                            <comment id="16609764" author="anshumg" created="Mon, 10 Sep 2018 20:28:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This new patch shouldn&apos;t break anything, but I&apos;ve added a more apt method plus fixed the javadoc. Running tests now and will commit after.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
