                            <comment id="16610577" author="ab" created="Tue, 11 Sep 2018 13:28:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Several tests already use &lt;tt&gt;CloudTestUtils.clusterShape(...)&lt;/tt&gt;, which provides more options, among others checking only active shards and checking for shard leaders - we should probably consolidate this code in one place.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
